{"tid":996281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲本名 陳云根，究竟有乜意思","createTime":"2019-01-26T07:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T07:56:00.000Z","uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9acfac67b090fbe7b42e9b23e021cad9812694b6","tid":996281,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時<br />\n我都係一名青山派信徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問都叫熟讀陳雲著作<br />\n<br />\n記得一次見到佢解釋自己起名嘅來由<br />\n大意係（出處唔記得咗）：<br />\n佢老豆幫佢改名做「雲（云）根」，意思係「巨石」咁解，不過用典太生僻，後來唔知村長定校長幫佢改名做陳文堅，後來寫專欄時編輯建議佢改筆名做陳雲<br />\n以前無聊<br />\n上網查到確實如此<br />\n又查《辭源》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRF8yyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRF8yyo.jpg&h=6cce863d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近突然想起<br />\n所以講幾句"},{"pid":"f1bc079050daf04c7d1c5df1a17a246f4a343401","tid":996281,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"陳石"},{"pid":"ef7833abe04692831b0ce01dfb1acddde95fe64c","tid":996281,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcf10a63c0d26ea75f4883a8c3bf867e21afc291","tid":996281,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"時事?"},{"pid":"bcf44075e90334d71ceb0b556e3921f2712829ff","tid":996281,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"文青上腦就仆去感情台吟詩作對啦"},{"pid":"97191e24d91869355d65b50c5870dc2e00850e15","tid":996281,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"問支那雞蟲講獨派HKVDC_2017"}]}